OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry across the south
OL,6,Fand east with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud and very warm sunny spells.
OL,8,FCloudier in the north and west with
OL,9,Fpatchy rain and drizzle, before more
OL,10,Fpersistent rain moves into the
OL,11,Fsouthwest later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain will move
OL,14,Fnortheast across many parts, turning
OL,15,Fheavy and persistent over western
OL,16,Fhills. Staying mostly dry in the
OL,17,Fsoutheast. Warm and muggy for many
OL,18,Fwith low cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
