OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,6,Frain and drizzle. Turning brighter in
OL,7,Fthe north and northwest with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers. Some warm bright spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping in the south. Humid in the
OL,10,Fsouth.
